title: Boost Relic
description: Legends say this could power an entire server...
accessibilityLabel: Boost Relic. Legends say this could power an entire server...

title: Cyberspace
description: Witness the entire world in motion.
accessibilityLabel: Cyberspace. Witness the entire world in motion.

title: Hydro Blast
accessibilityLabel: A powerful stream of water swirls and twirls in the air. Wait, where's it headed off to?!

title: Shatter
accessibilityLabel: Rippling flames travel across a layer of glass, shattering it. How bittersweet that the glass, molded by fire's embrace, be undone by the very flames that forged it.

title: Magic Hearts
accessibilityLabel: Hearts are beating and shimmering upon the profile, binding you under its charm.

title: Sakura Dreams
accessibilityLabel: Sakura petals gently flutter in the breeze under sunlight... a true display of nature's beauty and elegance.

title: Power Surge
description: You're about to witness true power.
accessibilityLabel: A surge of power erupts, surrounding the profile with an aura of intense energy. Those who gaze upon it will be left in awe.

title: Shuriken Strike
description: Every side is the pointy end.
accessibilityLabel: Three shurikens are thrown, spinning furiously until they finally strike their target. Ow, those must've hurt.

title: Mystic Vines
description: Why touch grass when you can touch magical vines?
accessibilityLabel: Magical vines grow and wrap around the outer edges of the profile. Is Mother Nature feeling extra affectionate today?

title: Pixie Dust
accessibilityLabel: Glimmering pixie dust and sparkles adorn the outer edges of the profile, casting a radiant glow.

title: Discord-Os
description: Bet you can't have just one bowl.
accessibilityLabel: Cereal and milk pour in from the heavens, flooding the profile in delicious, nutritious goodness. You can't beat the classics.

title: Breakfast Plate
description: The best meal for any time of day.
accessibilityLabel: Eggs, bacon, berries, and toast unite to form a breakfast meal, arranged with a smile. You can hear the bellies of profile admirers everywhere rumbling.

title: Ghoulish Graffiti
accessibilityLabel: Graffiti-esque stars are strobing across the profile. But wait, you notice there's something written in the stars... 'BOO!' Did we get ya?

title: Dark Omens
accessibilityLabel: A ghastly portal suddenly appears, summoning three ghostly spirits to haunt your enemies - no one gets to beat you in a game and get away with it.

title: Zombie Slime
description: I don't think you should touch that.
accessibilityLabel: Out of nowhere, a glob of slime suddently drops from above, forming into a skull before vaporizing in the air. Did someone just curse you?

title: Fall Foliage
accessibilityLabel: A cascade of orange and brown autumn leaves gently sway and fall from their trees towards the earth. Shall we make the biggest leaf pile the world has ever seen?

title: Lilypad Life
accessibilityLabel: Under drizzling rain, a frog hops onto a floating lilypad, then hops away... perhaps never to be seen again. Farewell, frog friend.

title: Midnight Lilypad Life
accessibilityLabel: Under dark midnight rain, a frog hops onto a floating lilypad, then hops away... perhaps never to be seen again. Farewell, frog friend.

title: Muddy Lilypad Life
accessibilityLabel: Under drizzling rain, a frog hops onto a lilypad floating on muddy water then hops away... perhaps never to be seen again. Farewell, frog friend.

title: Deck the halls
description: Keep out of reach from cats
accessibilityLabel: Festive string lights wrap around the user profile

title: Snowy Shenanigans
accessibilityLabel: In a sudden gust of snow and wind, a snowman sweeps into and out of view, leaving behind a flurry of snow in his wake. Who knows if we'll ever see him again...

title: Goozilla
description: Wait a second, what's my profile even made of?!
accessibilityLabel: A clawed paw slashes and tears through the profile. Out oozes... slimy green goo? Gross!

title: Heartzilla
description: Is this what they mean when they say love hurts?
accessibilityLabel: A clawed paw slashes and tears through the profile. Out floods... red hearts! How cute!

title: Monster Pop
accessibilityLabel: A purple, cheeky little creature floats across the screen. It's so adorable~~ wo-woah woahhh it just exploded!

title: Nightrunner
accessibilityLabel: A slick-looking car cruises through a futuristic city, dodging obstacles and speeding off in a neon glow of superspeed light.

title: Uplink Error
accessibilityLabel: Uh oh, looks like the data of this profile is fractured. Glitches flicker across screen in a series of surprisingly aesthetically pleasing colors.

title: Dragon Dance
description: No evil spirits on my watch.
accessibilityLabel: A dragon glides into view on top of the profile, circling a few times before taking rest at the very top.

title: Fortune Flurry
accessibilityLabel: A slew of red envelopes ride the wind and rush through the profile.

title: Midnight Celebration
accessibilityLabel: Fireworks ignite and light up the profile surrounded by ornamental designs.

title: Rock Slide
description: A ballet of rock and stone.
accessibilityLabel: A cascade of large rocks swirl into view, then settle around the frame of the profile. Talk about heavy lifting.

title: Vortex
description: Beware the eye of the storm.
accessibilityLabel: A giant whirlwind forms across the profile. Wouldn't want to get caught in the middle of that!

title: Mastery
accessibilityLabel: A mix of fire, water, earth, and wind swirl into the profile's view, then neatly settle around the profile's frame in perfect harmony.

title: Dreamy
accessibilityLabel: A radiant, dreamy aura of vibrant colors and glowing sparkles cover the profile, conveying the state of being in a happy dream.

title: Ki Detonate
accessibilityLabel: A ball of raw, powerful energy is about to detonate in the center of the profile and obliterate everything in its radius. We should probably be hiding behind something right now.

title: Sushi Mania
accessibilityLabel: A variety of sushi suddenly appears on the profile. Sushi lovers are ecstatic about this sudden occurrence.

title: Petal Serenade
accessibilityLabel: The profile comes alive with a burst of spring flowers that serenade the profile with colorful petals.

title: Fellowship of the Spring
description: They only gather around this time of the year.
accessibilityLabel: A gathering of spring bugs and insects bustle around the profile. One cannot help but think they seem to be pursuing an important mission to a faraway land...

title: Spring Bloom
accessibilityLabel: Cheerful thunderclouds release a gentle rain that awakens the dormant flowers around them into full bloom.

title: Clove's Ruse
description: Smoke's out. Time to make some mischief.
accessibilityLabel: Clove summons a sphere of smoke over the profile.

title: ACE
accessibilityLabel: A kill banner displaying 5 confirmed kills.

title: The Immortal Clove
description: They've got all the time in the world.
accessibilityLabel: Clove poses on the profile with fabulous style.

title: Study Spot
accessibilityLabel: A jumble of stationery and electronics appear on the profile, indicating a serious study session about to take place.

title: All Nighter
accessibilityLabel: A soft glare of morning light bathes a profile adorned with houseplants and stringlights.

title: Watercolors
description: When the world feels grey, add a splash of color.
accessibilityLabel: Soft, colorful circles illuminate the profile amid gentle raindrops.

title: Shooting Stars
accessibilityLabel: Several shooting stars streak across the profile - don't forget to make a wish!

title: Supernova
accessibilityLabel: A supernova explodes, leaving behind a glittering aftermath of stars.

title: Twilight
description: Is the universe winking at me?
accessibilityLabel: Twilight gently covers the profile, revealing twinkling stars.

title: Feelin' Mischievous
accessibilityLabel: A digital, goofy face zips onto the profile, blows a raspberry, and leaves behind a poop.

title: Feelin' 90s
description: Your uncle has a shirt just like this.
accessibilityLabel: Colorful shapes and patterns decorate the profile with good ol' fashioned 90's pizzazz.

title: Feelin' Pizzazz
accessibilityLabel: Colorful zigzags playfully decorate the profile's frame and centerspace.

title: Jolly Roger
description: Ye be warned... give no quarter.
accessibilityLabel: A black pirate flag depicting the famed Jolly Roger skull and crossbones gets slashed by a cutlass. Surely this means war!

title: Forgotten Treasure
description: Many a greedy eye be yearnin' for a peek... guard yer secrets closely.
accessibilityLabel: A treasure map detailing the location of buried treasure, with a curious skull marked along the path.

title: Haunted Man O' War
description: Sail Ho! We be in cursed waters now...
accessibilityLabel: A haunted Man O' War pirate ship eerily drifts across the profile, a sight that sends shivers down the spines of even the hardest of sailors.

title: Space Evader
description: That was the best flying I've seen to date - right up to the part where you got hit.
accessibilityLabel: A spaceship quickly barrelrolls out of the way from a barrage of laser fire. Unfortunately, it doesn't evade the follow up missile attack and gets taken out. Better luck next time.

title: Turbo Drive
description: Give your rivals a cheeky wave from the rearview.
accessibilityLabel: In its final lap, a racing car skillfully serves around the final corner before accelerating across the finish line to secure first place.

title: Twinkle Trails
description: Chase the stars to collect them all.
accessibilityLabel: Magical stars float into open view before traveling into surrounding pipes. Collect all the stars while they're out in the open!

title: Saya
description: A mysterious beauty blossoms under the moonlight.
accessibilityLabel: Saya appears over the profile, the glowing beauty of the crescent moon behind her. Wait... why do I hear boss music?

title: Wake Up!
description: You wash ashore on a strange island...
accessibilityLabel: Lamball, Cattiva, and Chikipi curiously poke their heads out to stare at the mysterious new face who just washed up on their island.

title: Tocotoco
accessibilityLabel: A Tocotoco suddenly emerges out of nowhere and waddles towards you before dramatically exploding. There goes your base, half your Pals, and hours of progress!

title: Arcane Summons
accessibilityLabel: A circular sigil inscribed with mysterious symbols appears, summoned by someone preparing to unleash its arcane power. Hope you got some magic resistance.

title: Vengeance
accessibilityLabel: A cursed skull engulfed in flames appears, staring at you with its mouth agape as if letting out an angry scream. Did someone just hex you?

title: Spirit Flame
accessibilityLabel: A ribbon of luminous, ethereal flame flares across the profile, illuminating it with a hauntingly beautiful glow.

title: NiCe pRoFiLE
accessibilityLabel: SpongeBob waddles onto the profile with his arms nested onto his hips like a chicken. He kicks off the ground a few times before rapidly flapping his arms and somehow flying away. Who showed him the plaid this time?

title: Handsome Squidward
accessibilityLabel: Squidward's handsome, chiseled face appears, and gives a charming wink. Handsome Squidward then proceeds to glide across the profile with an elegant, ballet-like twirl.

title: DoodleBob Takeover
accessibilityLabel: DoodleBob walks onto the profile holding a giant pencil. He lets out a roar of defiance and starts to maniacally erase the surface of the profile itself, revealing... flower clouds?! Have we been living in Bikini Bottom this entire time?

title: Plankton Splat
description: Stealing the Krabby Patty secret formula.
accessibilityLabel: Plankton angrily walks onto the middle of the profile when suddenly SpongeBob walks by and unknowingly squishes Plankton into a puddle with his shoe.

title: Ocean Flowers
accessibilityLabel: Several brightly colored ocean flowers pop up across the profile, now submerged with an underwater ambiance. Welcome to Bikini Bottom!

title: Yoru Dimensional Rip
description: Tear through the dimensional fabric and make your mark.
accessibilityLabel: The hands of Yoru appear over your profile. Yoru's masked face is visible for just a second before he succeeds in tearing open the dimensional fabric of your profile and seemingly vanishes.

title: VCT Supernova
description: Upgrade your look with a supernova of VCT 2024 style.
accessibilityLabel: The VALORANT Champions Tour logo appears over your profile, glowing and twirling with celestial energy before exploding in a supernova-like fashion, revealing the Champions 2024 Finisher.

title: Oni's Curse
accessibilityLabel: Out of fumes of smoke, the menacing face of an Oni demon appears and dashes towards those unfortunate enough to meet its gaze.

title: Of Ink and Steel
description: Words in ink, deeds in steel.
accessibilityLabel: A portrait in ink emerges on the profile, displaying a mysterious samurai warrior practicing their swordsmanship under a red sun before jumping off into the sunset.

title: Sakura Katana
description: May the blossoms guide your blade.
accessibilityLabel: A katana with cherry blossoms dancing around its blade twirls across the profile before dashing off towards an unfortunate target.

title: Chocolate Discord-Os
description: I know what you're thinking. But don't knock it till you try it.
accessibilityLabel: Chocolate milk and and brightly colored Discord-Os cereal pour into the profile, filling it to the brim like a giant, delicious bowl of breakfast goodness.

title: Heartzilla (Purple)
description: Is this what they mean when they say love hurts?
accessibilityLabel: The yellow claws of the massive Heartzilla slashes the profile, leaving a gash that releases a flurry of tiny, purple hearts.

title: Twilight Grove
description: Step inside and see autumn's beauty unfold.
accessibilityLabel: Lovely chrysanthemums decorate the frame of the profile, glowing softly as they shift colors from blue to fuchsia when touched by a pair of fluttering butterflies.

title: Sunrise Grove
description: Step inside and see autumn's beauty unfold.
accessibilityLabel: Lovely peach-colored chrysanthemums decorate the frame of the profile, shining brightly in sunlight as monarch butterflies flutter around them.

title: Autumn Equinox
description: Autumn's arrival is written in the stars.
accessibilityLabel: Gold and blue petals decorate the frame the avatar as the earth, sun, and moon appear and align in a cosmic dance that teases the arrival of autumn.

title: Sun and Moon
description: When you're staring at the sky, watching the heavens in motion... do you ever just marvel at the wonder of it all?
accessibilityLabel: Our fiery, molten sun gracefully spins and transforms into the glowing moon across profile.

title: Scarlet Fall Foliage
accessibilityLabel: A cascade of red, autumn leaves gently sway and fall from their trees towards the earth. Shall we make the biggest leaf pile the world has ever seen?

title: Woodland Fall Foliage
accessibilityLabel: A cascade of red, green, and yellow, autumn leaves gently sway and fall from their trees towards the earth. Shall we make the biggest leaf pile the world has ever seen?

title: Street Fighter 6
description: The award winning Street Fighter 6 theme!
accessibilityLabel: The Street Fighter 6 wordmark is splashed across the profile with a vibrant, graffiti-like art style, adding a street-savvy flair to the profile.

title: Akuma's Wrath
description: Messatsu! Feel the power of the Satsui no hado!
accessibilityLabel: Akuma's imposing figure appears over the profile, his back turned as dark, demonic energy radiates from him. His presence makes him a mighty ally for imposing fear and respect amongst one's profile admirers.

title: M. Bison's Return
accessibilityLabel: M. Bison hovers menacingly over the profile in his signature red military uniform, radiating purple energy with his arms crossed, eyes glowing fiercely, and his iconic devilish grin on his face.

title: Classic Street Fighter
description: Bring it back to the retro streets!
accessibilityLabel: Ryus classic retro portrait from Street Fighter 2 appears over the profile, with the legendary phrase 'You must defeat Sheng Long to stand a chance' written out beneath it.

title: Blazing Ghoulish Graffiti
accessibilityLabel: Graffiti-esque stars in burnt orange are strobing across the profile. But wait, you notice there's something written in the stars... "BOO!" Did we get ya?

title: Neon Ghoulish Graffiti
accessibilityLabel: Graffiti-esque stars in neon blues and yellows are strobing across the profile. But wait, you notice there's something written in the stars... "BOO!" Did we get ya?

title: Infernal Dark Omens
accessibilityLabel: A ghastly infernal portal suddenly appears, summoning three blazing, ghostly spirits to haunt your enemies - no one gets to beat you in a game and get away with it.

title: Midnight Dark Omens
accessibilityLabel: A ghastly blue portal suddenly appears, summoning three ghostly spirits to haunt your enemies - no one gets to beat you in a game and get away with it.

title: Bubblegum Zombie Slime
description: I don't think you should touch that.
accessibilityLabel: Out of nowhere, a glob of pink slime suddently drops from above, forming into a skull before vaporizing in the air. Did someone just curse you?

title: Midnight Zombie Slime
description: I don't think you should touch that.
accessibilityLabel: Out of nowhere, a glob of blue slime suddently drops from above, forming into a skull before vaporizing in the air. Did someone just curse you?

title: D20 Roll
description: You win some, you lose some. This effect can show your profile admirers one of two random outcomes.
accessibilityLabel: A 20-sided dice rolls into view, displaying 'Critical Failure' when landing on a 1, and 'Critical Success' when rolling a 20. The outcome it decides remains unknown to this day.

title: Red Dragon
accessibilityLabel: A fearsome red dragon swoops into view, breathing flames that engulf the entire profile in a fiery inferno before vanishing in the flames.

title: Beholder
description: Arent you a sight to behold!
accessibilityLabel: Multiple glowing eyes appear until a menacing Beholder fully reveals itself in the dark, firing a deadly laser of arcane energy from its central eye.

title: Mimic
accessibilityLabel: A treasure chest falls from above but... surprise! The treasure chest reveals itself to be a Mimic that lashes its giant purple tongue out and bares rows upon rows of razor-sharp teeth.
